{"type": "root", "attrs": {"type": "node", "context": "sop", "internal": "labs::wfc_initialize", "icon": "wfc_intialize", "tags": "model, gamedev, sidefxlabs", "version": null, "namespace": "labs"}, "body": [{"level": 0, "type": "title", "indent": 0, "text": ["Labs WFC Initialize Grid"], "extent": [0, 29]}, {"type": "summary", "indent": 0, "text": [" A utility tool to initialize a WFC grid to be used with the WFC Solver "], "extent": [145, 225]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["The WFC Initialize Grid tool is a convenient way of setting up a grid to be used as the sample or output grid for the WFC Solver node.\nIt sets up the required attributes in the correct way for the solver."], "extent": [225, 431]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["When using this tool to create an output grid or manually set up the values for a sample grid, the constraint multiparm should be used.\nThis allows you to select points and assign a custom value, which might be desired for making tweaks to an imported sample texture. For the output grid this is useful for setting constraints for the solver."], "extent": [431, 775]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["See: ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/labs--2d_wavefunctioncollapse", "type": "link", "text": ["WFC Solver"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/labs--2d_wavefunctioncollapse"}], "extent": [775, 833]}, {"level": 1, "id": "parameters", "container": true, "type": "parameters_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [833, 845], "body": [{"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 4, "text": ["Grid Resolution"], "extent": [845, 871], "body": [{"type": "parameters_item_group", "body": [{"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["From Texture"], "extent": [871, 889], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["When turned on, the grid resolution will be automatically calculated based on the specified texture resolution."], "extent": [889, 1009]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Texture"], "extent": [1009, 1022], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["The texture to be used for initializing the WFC grid."], "extent": [1022, 1084]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Rows"], "extent": [1084, 1094], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["The number of rows in your grid."], "extent": [1094, 1135]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Columns"], "extent": [1135, 1148], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["The number of columns in your grid."], "extent": [1148, 1192]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}]}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 3, "text": ["Overrides"], "extent": [1192, 1211], "body": [{"type": "parameters_item_group", "body": [{"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 3, "text": ["Selection"], "extent": [1211, 1225], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 6, "text": ["The group string to apply an override value to."], "extent": [1225, 1279]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 3, "text": ["Value"], "extent": [1279, 1289], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 6, "text": ["The value to be assigned to the specified selection."], "extent": [1289, 1352]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}]}], "text": "Parameters"}], "title": ["Labs WFC Initialize Grid"], "summary": [" A utility tool to initialize a WFC grid to be used with the WFC Solver "]}